{"id":580435,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/03/【老乡别跑】宣布修宪两周后，移民仍为敏感/","date":"2018-03-10T07:50:48Z","modified":"2018-03-10T08:44:49Z","title":"【老乡别跑】宣布修宪两周后，“移民”仍为敏感内容","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>距2月25日宣布<del>登基</del><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/%e4%b8%89%e4%b8%ad%e5%85%a8%e4%bc%9a/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">修宪</a>已近2周，<strong>微博“移民”搜索结果仍然只显示蓝V账号内容，在知乎上则不显示任何结果，百度指数依旧“暂不提供数据”。</strong></p>\n<p>2018年2月25日，<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E5%8D%81%E4%B9%9D%E5%B1%8A%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%A8%E4%BC%9A\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">中共中央提议修改宪法</a>，取消国家主席任期限制。消息一出，舆论哗然，大量网民迅速开始在社交网站上发表嘲讽、反对修宪的言论。铺天盖地的负面评论很快让网络审查者喘不过气，除<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/02/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e5%8c%85%e5%ad%90%e7%99%bb%e5%9f%ba%e6%96%b0%e6%b5%aa%e5%be%ae%e5%8d%9a%e8%a2%ab%e5%88%a0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af%e5%ad%98%e6%a1%a3/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">大面积删帖</a>、设置<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/02/%e3%80%90%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e8%af%8d%e5%ba%93%e3%80%91%e5%90%be%e7%9a%87%e4%b8%87%e5%b2%81%e5%8a%9d%e8%bf%9b%e7%99%bb%e5%9f%ba%e7%ad%89%e4%b9%a0/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">微博禁发词</a>和<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/02/%e3%80%90%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e8%af%8d%e5%ba%93%e3%80%91%e6%90%9c%e7%b4%a2%e6%ad%aa%e8%84%96%e5%ad%90%e6%a0%91%e4%b8%8d%e8%a6%81%e8%84%b8%e5%8d%83%e7%a7%8b/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">搜索禁词</a>外，审查者还采取了<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/02/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e4%bf%ae%e5%ae%aa%e7%99%bb%e5%9f%ba%e8%af%9d%e9%a2%98-%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c%e8%a8%80%e8%ae%ba%e6%8e%a7%e5%88%b6%e6%8e%aa%e6%96%bd%e4%b8%80%e8%a7%88/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">更多辅助手段进行言论控制</a>，如社交平台禁止修改用户名、头像等个人信息；甚至有网游也无法修改用户名；百度搜索不提供“移民“等关键词数据；微博搜索结果白名单化，只显示蓝V账号内容等。</p>\n<p>另外，有名为<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/I2JImFrtcvDAGiWDVTuwNQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">“梓泉”的微信公号爆料</a>称，其朋友的一家美国月子中心的官方微博突然遭到销号，疑似是因为微博近期开始对出国/移民服务账号进行限制。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_580438\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/阑夕.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-580438\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/阑夕.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"341\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/阑夕.jpg 1220w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/阑夕-300x186.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/阑夕-768x476.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/阑夕-1024x635.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">微博截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_580437\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎-1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-580437\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"402\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎-1.jpg 1578w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎-1-300x219.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎-1-768x561.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎-1-1024x748.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">知乎搜索“移民”不会返回任何结果；网页版截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_580439\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/百度指数.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-580439\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/百度指数.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"121\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/百度指数.jpg 1244w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/百度指数-300x66.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/百度指数-768x169.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/百度指数-1024x226.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">百度搜素指数结果截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_580436\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/微博搜索-移民.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-580436\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/微博搜索-移民.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"4858\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/微博搜索-移民.jpg 1276w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/微博搜索-移民-31x300.jpg 31w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/微博搜索-移民-768x7462.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">微博“移民”搜索结果只显示来自蓝V账号的内容；微博截图</span></p></div>\n<p><strong>附：</strong>微信公号“梓泉”(ID: ziquanM) 贴出的聊天记录</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/移民1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-580442\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/移民1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"569\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/移民1.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/移民1-211x300.jpg 211w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/移民1-768x1092.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/移民1-720x1024.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[34076,21411,34052,30129,32609,33535,25497,31267]}